data.text:
baha the information company

baha is a leading provider of real-time market data, financial news, technology and solutions for the financial industry. baha offers real-time data terminals for professionals, global financial market data covering over 12 million financial instruments on more than 150 exchanges, as well as 24/7 breaking news with global coverage and free web and mobile apps. From a total of around 200 real-time data providers worldwide, only Reuters 1851, Bloomberg 1981 and now baha in 2021 were named after the founder.
